doctype html
html(lang="en")
  include ../includes/head.pug
  title Sewa Kapal
  body
    include ../includes/header.pug
            
    #index-banner.parallax-container     
      .section.no-pad-bot
        .container
          br
          br
          h1.header.center.white-text.text-lighten-2=judul
          .row.center
            h5.header.col.s12.light.white-text.text-lighten-2 "Petualangan tanpa batas di hamparan samudera"
          .row.center
            a#download-button.btn-large.waves-effect.waves-light.lighten-1(href=kategoriKapal class= `${colorTheme}`) mulai
      .parallax
        img.responsive-img(src='public/img/site/bg-main.jpg' alt='Background Image')


    // nanti buat card promo2...
    .container
          .section
            .row#row
              .col.s4(style='min-width: 15em;')
                .card.z-depth-2
                  .card-image.waves-effect.waves-block.waves-light
                    img#gambar.activator.responsive-img(src='public/img/site/item3.jpg', alt='Boat', onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='/public/img/site/noshippic.png';", style='width:100%;height:14.8em;object-fit: cover;')
                  .card-content
                    span#nama.card-title.activator.text-darken-4(class='${htmlColor}-text') Jaminan Kualitas
                  .card-reveal
                    span#model.card-title.text-darken-4(class='${htmlColor}-text')
                      | Kualitas
                      i.material-icons.right close
                    p#tipe.text-darken-4(class='${htmlColor}-text') Kami memperhatikan pengelolaan kualitas dengan serius. Ini berarti kami memberikan perhatian ketat untuk memastikan standar kualitas tertinggi pada lingkungan kami setiap waktu.

              .col.s4(style='min-width: 15em;')
                .card.z-depth-2
                  .card-image.waves-effect.waves-block.waves-light
                    img#gambar.activator.responsive-img(src='public/img/site/item1.jpg', alt='Boat', onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='/public/img/site/noshippic.png';", style='width:100%;height:14.8em;object-fit: cover;')
                  .card-content
                    span#nama.card-title.activator.text-darken-4(class='${htmlColor}-text') Sesuai Kebutuhan
                  .card-reveal
                    span#model.card-title.text-darken-4(class='${htmlColor}-text')
                      | Kebutuhan
                      i.material-icons.right close
                    p#tipe.text-darken-4(class='${htmlColor}-text') Sesuai dengan kebutuhan dan perkembangan bisnis, kami menyediakan berbagai jenis kapal hingga kebutuhan yang spesifik.

              .col.s4(style='min-width: 15em;')
                .card.z-depth-2
                  .card-image.waves-effect.waves-block.waves-light
                    img#gambar.activator.responsive-img(src='public/img/site/item2.jpg', alt='Boat', onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='/public/img/site/noshippic.png';", style='width:100%;height:14.8em;object-fit: cover;')
                  .card-content
                    span#nama.card-title.activator.text-darken-4(class='${htmlColor}-text') Navigasi Akurat
                  .card-reveal
                    span#model.card-title.text-darken-4(class='${htmlColor}-text')
                      | Navigasi
                      i.material-icons.right close
                    p#tipe.text-darken-4(class='${htmlColor}-text') Mengintegrasikan perangkat navigasi kokpit ke desain all-in-one, yang menjadi sangat handal. Menjamin pelayaran dengan rasa aman dan kestabilan.
      
      
    .parallax-container.valign-wrapper
      .section.no-pad-bot
        .container
          .row.center
            h5.header.col.s12.light.white-text Keperluan komersil maupun pribadi, kami siap membantu anda.
      .parallax
        img.responsive-img(src='public/img/site/bg-main2.jpg' alt='Background Image 2')
       

    //dibawah kasih paralax lg

    include ../includes/footer.pug
    include ../includes/loginmodal.pug
    include ../includes/script.pug   